title: Photos: Minooka versus Plainfield South football
text:
Photos: Minooka versus Plainfield South football Published: Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015 2:40 a.m. CDT Caption (Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com) The Minooka Indians run through a cloud of fog before the start of their game against Plainfield South Friday, Oct. 9, at Minooka High School in Minooka. The Cougars beat the Indians, 34-27. Photo by Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com. Caption (Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com) A wave of Plainfield South defenders brings down Minooka's Drew Turek Friday, Oct. 9, at Minooka High School in Minooka. The Cougars beat the Indians, 34-27. Photo by Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com. Caption (Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com) Minooka's Michael Malinowski plows through Plainfield South's Mitchell Ganassin while running the ball Friday, Oct. 9, at Minooka High School in Minooka. The Cougars beat the Indians, 34-27. Photo by Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com. Caption (Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com) Plainfield South's Jake Portz topples Minooka's Johnny Carnagio Friday, Oct. 9, at Minooka High School in Minooka. The Cougars beat the Indians, 34-27. Photo by Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com. Caption (Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com) Members of the Minooka High School band before during the first quarter o Minooka's game against Plainfield South Friday, Oct. 9, at Minooka High School in Minooka. The Cougars beat the Indians, 34-27. Photo by Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com. Caption (Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com) Minooka's Joshua Garcia falls under the force of Plainfield Souths defense Friday, Oct. 9, at Minooka High School in Minooka. The Cougars beat the Indians, 34-27. Photo by Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com. Caption (Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com) Minooka's Joshua Garcia evades several Plainfield South's Tyler Jensen Friday, Oct. 9, at Minooka High School in Minooka. The Cougars beat the Indians, 34-27. Photo by Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com. Caption (Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com) Minooka's Johnny Carnagio outruns Plainfield South's Eric Johnson while looking for an opening to pass Friday, Oct. 9, at Minooka High School in Minooka. The Cougars beat the Indians, 34-27. Photo by Eric Ginnard - eginnard@shawmedia.com.
